{"tid":841061,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【幣少又贏】比特大陸遞上市申請 半年賺58億","createTime":"2018-09-29T09:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T10:00:15.000Z","uid":5063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2c5058b3bc79583e999bc004e2a6327b352b100e","tid":841061,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:45:41.000Z","msg":"從事設計加密貨幣挖礦芯片的比特大陸，今日上載初步上市申請文件，擬以同股不同權形式上市；分為1股1票的A股和1股10票的B股。<br />\n<br />\n公司指，業務涵蓋比特幣、比特幣現金、以太幣等，為少數幾家多種加密貨幣提供挖礦解決方案的公司之一。至2018年6月，公司半年收入為28.45億美元，股東應佔溢利為7.42億美元(約58億港元)，同比增8倍，經調整EBITDA為11.23億美元。毛利率為36.2%，較去年全年跌12個百份點。<br />\n<br />\n按2017年收入計，比特大陸為全球第4大無晶圓廠ASIC芯片設計公司；更為全球最大基於ASIC的加密貨幣礦機公司，佔全球74.5%市場份額。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是，已經以同股不同權上市的新股小米(1810)及美團(3690)，上市不足一周已先後跌穿招股價。目前仍有找鋼網已入表申請以同股不同權形式上市。<br />\n<br />\n中金公司為獨家保薦人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180926/58727263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F58727263&d=Rk%2FbIM7tdILA6ESJHrBbmL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=6b487f2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F58727263&h=1c9f13e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180926/58727263</a><br />\n<br />\n如果真係上到（而且機會幾大，我check過2018年半年賺得多過2017年全年），叫人投資礦場班友又可以借d易叫人買，唔知又可以撿幾多呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa54b81521cff925ba2ff60e3e677e71727f657e","tid":841061,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:49:26.000Z","msg":"我都賺夠了 想俾其他人賺下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c790c81675b93a2d68fa7fd460c585bad406f75b","tid":841061,"uid":53206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:49:58.000Z","msg":"弊少幾時上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd5dfe5268d259cc1148ae85d81e1be8fb6a90a","tid":841061,"uid":38535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:40:21.000Z","msg":"呢隻真係想put爆佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望會出輪"},{"pid":"b8ff8195d9eec2ad4b7afac03b241f3266924c5b","tid":841061,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edd5dfe5268d259cc1148ae85d81e1be8fb6a90a","tid":841061,"uid":38535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:40:21.000Z","msg":"呢隻真係想put爆佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望會出輪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:57:29.000Z","msg":"實會啦，即刻又話納入恆指xx指數嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd64f4d05c5c7d346857702869658ce305c48c0f","tid":841061,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:20:14.000Z","msg":"岩岩出院 瑠軍話要屌米股東執一個開<br />\n<br />\n屌米升左一倍未？"},{"pid":"0409098d4434ca9ef4563710ef154c5840d513a5","tid":841061,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/190839_19bcd1a729db73cac9c8086ddb749b1d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F190839_19bcd1a729db73cac9c8086ddb749b1d.png&h=69525271&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}